{"tid":2255483,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"應該禁止係巴士煲電話粥","createTime":"2020-10-23T14:42:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-23T17:33:35.000Z","uid":356767,"like":50,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c5d60503b3e3c6d35fbdaa258d16b801bda3fb24","tid":2255483,"uid":356767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T14:42:19.000Z","msg":"我覺得係公共交通到唔騷擾其他乘客係基本禮儀啦<br />\n屌 原來唔撚係<br />\n翻工放工可以坐巴士靜靜地聽下歌本來幾開心<br />\n點知啲阿嬋阿叔成撚日大大聲煲電話粥<br />\n唔係一兩句就收線 係講足成程！！<br />\n有冇諗過成車人都對你啲私事冇興趣<br />\n頭先後面個阿嬸仲要拉低口罩講野 我睥過去佢先拉翻個口罩 但仲係不改聲線繼續講電話 過一陣又除口罩<br />\n我屌你老母 比翻啲質素得唔得<br />\n放工已經攰 想訓翻陣都唔得 拎支咪比你講野好唔好？？"},{"pid":"4e92537d91126c2b78203891881ad73ab179ec76","tid":2255483,"uid":78703,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T14:43:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RSHziqJWYcM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRSHziqJWYcM&d=Z0jJ2Ci5UPqU8nDHOGo4vD11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=dcd2b875\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RSHziqJWYcM</a>"},{"pid":"d2f796d5d2312640fc0e9fb4736626713b85ea70","tid":2255483,"uid":99700,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T14:46:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j66jjDz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj66jjDz.jpg&h=9d8cc52a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a430717db96261f890d907cfb93ad212a1388155","tid":2255483,"uid":55851,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T14:49:50.000Z","msg":"仲要啲廢老對話係好on9，表達能力極差，講半個鐘都可能係重覆講緊同一樣野，聽到人都燥埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17aef1268ada5659b8d55bdd240360aeee14b751","tid":2255483,"uid":8435,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T14:53:43.000Z","msg":"啲廢老好鍾意同一段錄音聽幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能係隻耳唔靈又或者段嘢太長消化唔切<br />\n次次都好想講返一次俾佢聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e96a8